  "text": "Omalizumab is a recombinant humanized monoclonal antibody that blocks the highaffinity Fc receptor of IgE. Omalizumab has been approved for the treatment of moderate to severe asthma. However, there is currently more and more data showing promising results in the management of patients suffering from other allergic conditions such as chronic urticaria [CITATION_1] . Omalizumab is usually recommended when other systemic therapies have failed [3] .",
